Sennheiser has unveiled a new set of earphones, the Momentum True Wireless. The Bluetooth earphones are punted as truly wireless, and feature a touch interface and voice command support. Sennheiser has packed 7mm dynamic drivers into the earphones and promises four hours of battery life. The headphones are then charged when placed into their compact case with integrated powerbank. This provides a further 12 hours of usage, said Sennheiser. The Momentum True Wireless earphones will be available from November 2018 for 299 euros.